headline: Kimco Realty and Bozzuto Break Ground on The Chester at Westlake, Daly City's First New Mixed-Use Apartment Community in 15 Years
summary: Bozzuto, in partnership with Kimco Realty (NYSE: KIM), today announced the start of construction for The Chester at Westlake, a landmark mixed-use development that will be Daly City's first major predominantly market-rate apartment community in more than 15 years. Scheduled to open in winter 2027, the community will bring thoughtfully designed residences, dynamic amenities and a vibrant sense of place to one of the Bay Area's most established planned communities.
